text: haey pitabrakd nasa brasenbae yeung ban bamphlanh puok ke daoy tearounakamm namuoy mounnung vea( banhchoun mou ham meat mk)puokke pitchea niyeay tha ao mcheasa robsa puok yeung. hetoaveibeanchea trong min banhchoun anakneasar mneak mk aoy puok yeung daembi yeung nung thveuteam ayeat robsa trong mounnung puok yeung trauv abaon ning ameasamoukh
